{"tid":2150019,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"方保僑：美國推「潔淨網絡」影響香港數據中心地位","createTime":"2020-08-10T17:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T06:39:56.000Z","uid":225931,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5ce342afb818c8c502b335d37c6c32c5b090e704","tid":2150019,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T17:58:31.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）日前公佈「潔淨網絡計劃」（The Clean Network program），在五大網絡領域，包括應用程式、應用商店、雲端服務、流動網絡及海底互聯網電纜上，要求部分「不可信任」的中國企業於美國營運，以保障美國國民的私隱及企業的敏感資料。<br />\n<br />\n方保僑於節目中表示，計劃影響甚廣，內地公司製造的應用程式或需要在美國下架，亦會影響中資的數據中心及雲端服務，而早前美國FCC（聯邦通信委員會）基於國安考量，不批准由Google與Facebook聯手建設的太平洋光纖網路連到香港，亦會令科技企業改設數據中心到其他地方，對香港影響十分大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/30F2f2e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30F2f2e&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lKEelou7VeK%2FuoOlBiwx%2FXk%3D&h=a1338a70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/30F2f2e</a>"},{"pid":"46638735c19aadb0395e2255d8e48fde60106231","tid":2150019,"uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T18:28:31.000Z","msg":"咁香港應該加快同内地融合先得"},{"pid":"285cd394bd60d45644822208ababac206bcddd5a","tid":2150019,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T18:30:22.000Z","msg":"由美國唔肯鋪條光纖過香港  已經注定冇得做數據中心啦"},{"pid":"34557561686c503cb1fc8309b8e9356b9f98e58e","tid":2150019,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T18:31:39.000Z","msg":"將軍澳數據中心d it狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e02584cae5d43740df168d66fc8c9945e89d6ce","tid":2150019,"uid":279835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T18:32:43.000Z","msg":"香港只會喺dirty network嗰邊，仲做咩數據中心&hellip;&hellip; 有&hellip;&hellip;人面監察數據中心，DNA大數據分析&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"91396261d3598fc87f923bdb43dddbe67c2a8a9b","tid":2150019,"